===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# An [[unsteady]] [[motion]].
#:''The fat man walked down the street with a '''wobble'''.''
# A [[tremulous]] [[sound]].
#:''There was a '''wobble''' on her high notes.''

====Synonyms====
*(''unsteady motion''): [[jiggle]], [[quiver]], [[shake]], [[tremble]]
*(''tremulous sound''): [[quaver]], [[tremble]], [[tremolo]], [[vibrato]]

